<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a1628" />
    <title>Offline — broodwar.live</title>
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #060c18;
        color: #e2e5ea;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      }
      .container {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 28rem;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 4rem;
        height: 4rem;
        margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.4;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        color: #e2e5ea;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: rgba(226, 229, 234, 0.4);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      button {
        padding: 0.625rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(226, 229, 234, 0.1);
        background: rgba(226, 229, 234, 0.05);
        color: #e2e5ea;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      button:hover { background: rgba(226, 229, 234, 0.1); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="" class="logo" />
      <h1>You're offline</h1>
      <p>broodwar.live needs an internet connection for live data, replays, and streams. Check your connection and try again.</p>
      <button onclick="window.location.reload()">Retry</button>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
